### Pobierz pracownika o ID 1
GET {{host}}/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Pobierz pracownika o ID 1 z relacjami
GET {{host}}/api/employees/1?include=company
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Pobierz pracownika o ID 1 z wybranymi polami
GET {{host}}/api/employees/1?fields=first_name,last_name,email,position
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Pobierz pracownik√≥w konkretnej firmy
GET {{host}}/api/companies/1/employees
Content-Type: application/json
